social_posts.post_text: Cheers to The Syrings 🥂💍

League Champs, #1 in the state (4A-6A total) for academics sitting at a 3.92 cumulative GPA as a TEAM, and went through all of league with only 1 loss. 

This team is so special. They deserve every bit of this spotlight and recognition for their hard work. As our family always says.. hard work pays off ❤️
Just you, me and lots of husky hair on our clothes 🤍 So thankful for you and all we’ve built together. 488 days 💍

My girls. My team. 
This season is brutal. The weeks are long, school is longer and these girls push through mentally and physically as they grind non stop for months. Not only have they shown strength on the field, but they maintain over a 3.9 GPA as an entire team. Each day we work harder and harder to get better and they don’t get enough credit for the hours they work on and off the field. 

We just won our second round of playoffs off of a crazy comeback, and I just felt like the bragging was needed. I’m so proud of these girls (plus a few not pictured). I’d give them the world if I could. They make me a better coach every day.
Pios forever ❣️
Crumbl & rain delays ☔️
Let ‘er BUCK 🇺🇸❤️
As long as you’re right here 🤍

Laguna sunsets & my person 🤍 
Lucky for this life. Lucky to have you.

Soaking up this Cali sunshine with my better half ☀️

Accessibility in laguna 🤙🏽 thanks for the awesome power chair! For free to rent 7am to 5:30pm. Check it out!
Leaving Cali sun kissed and feeling so loved by you ☀️
Chasing all of the summer sunsets with you 🌅
I’m so proud of you 🤍
Getting to ride with my man for the first time ever was so special 🏔️🤍 so thankful

It’s been an amazing few days 🤍 
Thank you to @hi5sfoundation and @motodemption for inviting Andrew back to ride for redemption #2! These people and what they do.. we have no words. Just thank you for everything, and thank you for getting Andrew back doing what he loves most.

My Mads 💖 
You’ve been waiting for this moment for so long, and I’m so excited to meet miss baby Ray and add another dancer to our girl gang. Seeing you so happy and so radiant is the biggest blessing. Thank you Dan for making my besties future so bright and happy, you both are amazing for each other! What an amazing day celebrating the most loved and wished for little beeb! 🥹

365 Days until we say “I do” 💍
9/21/24 🤍
